data.description: Welcome to a beautiful corner lot home 5-bedroom, 3 full-bathroom sanctuary nestled in a serene neighborhood! This meticulously crafted home boasts a harmonious blend of comfort and elegance, featuring both hardwood and carpet flooring that adds warmth and sophistication throughout.  Step inside to discover a spacious layout designed for modern living, where natural light dances effortlessly through every room. The heart of the home is a chef's dream kitchen, equipped with sleek appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining.  Escape to your own private oasis in the backyard, where a charming pergola beckons you to unwind and entertain amidst lush greenery. Whether hosting summer BBQs or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars, this outdoor retreat is sure to delight family and friends alike.  With 5 generously sized bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and sitting room, there's no shortage of comfort or style in this residence. Don't miss your chance to make cherished memories in this exceptional property. Schedule your private showing today!"
